a thickness-adjusting layer for setting the thickness of the liquid crystal layer to be smaller in at least a portion of the reflective display region than in at least a portion of the transmissive display region, the thickness-adjusting layer including a sloping section, the reflective-display color filter and the transmissive-display color filter being disposed over at least a portion of the other of the reflective-display color filter and the transmissive-display color filter at the sloping section.

